title: Jenkins and Jonez - Kyrie’s Beautiful Game, Ciara in Denver, and Giant Spiders Raining From the Sky
itunes:title: Jenkins and Jonez - Kyrie’s Beautiful Game, Ciara in Denver, and Giant Spiders Raining From the Sky
description:
The guys discuss the intersection of gambling and sports highlighted by Calvin Ridley, Kyrie’s incredible 50 point game, the implications of Russell Wilson being traded to Denver, Netflix raising their prices, giant spiders on the east coast, and much more.
